Damn, why am I
remembering this?

6
00:00:28,220 --> 00:00:30,300
Does Bin like
doing things like this?

7
00:00:42,700 --> 00:00:44,140
What are you doing?

8
00:00:45,060 --> 00:00:46,190
Keep your distance.

9
00:00:50,460 --> 00:00:53,460
I'm gay,
not infected with COVID.

10
00:00:53,620 --> 00:00:57,100
Hey, don't come near me.

11
