just like in straight relationships.

15
00:01:19,500 --> 00:01:23,500
Your type?
Is it Bai Tian?

16
00:01:23,500 --> 00:01:26,420
That guy you made come?

17
00:01:29,180 --> 00:01:31,980
Mind your own business.
Definitely not someone like you.

18
00:01:31,980 --> 00:01:37,380
Oh, not my type?
Then I can sleep peacefully.

19
00:01:51,580 --> 00:01:57,220
Graduated middle school from Choraviti School,
the same as mine.

20
00:01:57,220 --> 00:02:00,620
Then moved to America for high school.

21
00:02:00,620 --> 00:02:05,300
After finishing his studies in America,
he returned to Thailand.

22
00:02:05,500 --> 00:02:07,900
His name is Max.
That name sounds familiar.

23
00:02:08,979 --> 00:02:10,139
Damn.

24
00:02:11,020 --> 00:02:13,860
Is that fat guy from Class 1
Max?

